{
  "design_notes": "S0 (Intro) introduces a driving synth bassline utilizing 4-beat hold notes that alternate on the outer lanes, interspersed with gentle melodic taps on the off-beats to establish an immersive rhythm. S1 (Drop) features the full drum kit and lead melody; kicks are mapped strictly to the center BAR lane while snares/claps alternate between GAP and NOTE to create physical contrast, and the melody is mapped to flowing lane sweeps that vary bar-by-bar to avoid repetition. S2 (Outro) drives the energy to its peak with a high-density drum roll and rapid synth runs across all three lanes, mapping every key onset up to the final beat of the audio track.",
  "sections": [
    {
      "name": "Intro",
      "start_bar": 0,
      "intent": "Introduce the synth bassline and set a clean, readable rhythm."
    },
    {
      "name": "Drop",
      "start_bar": 7,
      "intent": "Deliver high-energy drum physical contrast and flowing melodic sweeps."
    },
    {
      "name": "Outro",
      "start_bar": 15,
      "intent": "Drive the climax with a rolling build-up ending on a final dramatic accent."
    }
  ],
